Package edu.stanford.cfuller.imageanalysistools.meta.parameters

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ParameterParser
    Utilities for processing analysis parameters from suitably formatted files.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LegacyParameterXMLParser
    Utilities for processing analysis parameters from suitably formatted XML files; this processor uses the old format, which is just a list of parameter elements inside some root element.
    Parameter
    Represents a single parameter used for data analysis, with a name, a display name, a type, a value, and optionally a description.
    ParameterDictionary
    Represents a set of String keys, and associated parameter objects that specify various parameters for the analysis and their values.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ParameterType
    Parameters for storage in a ParameterDictionary can be one of four types: boolean, integer, floating-point, or String.
